#. Description of the theme
#: style.css
msgid "A purpose-built block theme for personal blogs, designed around portrait featured images and crafted for clear, readable content. Shanti is ideal for documenting life, travel, or thoughts — with simple layouts, generous spacing, and no visual clutter. Built entirely with WordPress blocks and Full Site Editing, it gives you full creative control while letting your words take center stage."
